FEATURED INWHAT IS WOOLF® DRIVEAfter the extraordinary success of WOOLF®, the world's first wearable device for driving dedicated to bikers, we are ready to introduce WOOLF® Drive, the new driving assistant designed for car drivers.WOOLF® Drive is an innovative accessory that perfectly fits inside your car, positioned directly on the steering wheel. It informs you about the presence of speed cameras and other sensitive points thanks to discreet vibration alerts, avoiding to distract you while driving with annoying sound or visual alarms that can reveal dangerous. WOOLF® Drive will signal you when to slow down near fixed and mobile speed cams, notifying you of new locations but remembering also the old ones on well-known routes, which you can often forget about.HOW IT WORKSWOOLF® Drive uses the same technology employed by the motorcycle version, classified Accessory of the year 2016 according to the readers of Motociclismo (second classified).Alerts are performed through an accurate localization system and thanks to the Bluetooth® connection with your device. Once you paired WOOLF® Drive with the dedicated App through a simple wizard you will no longer have to worry about downloading daily updates, maps or routes; WOOLF® Drive will do it for you. Daily updates of the speedcam database will automatically run directly from your phone. The automatic updating of App services will be free of charge anytime for all campaign supporters.The application developed by the team requires an active connection only during the upgrade phase, while in mobility it does not require constant data connection, but only active GPS positioning and Bluetooth®, ensuring in this way the operation in non-covered areas, minimizing data traffic consumption and optimizing your smartphone battery performance. VERSIONSWOOLF® Drive is available in 5 different versions designed to perfectly fit inside your car, harmoniously adapting to your style. The catalog includes 3 Leather versions and 2 versions in Premium Synthetic Leather. WOOLF® Drive guarantees a design aimed to fully match with the interior of different cars models. APPWOOLF® Drive guarantees you the maximum ease of use. All you have to do is pair it through bluetooth with its dedicated app and place it on the steering wheel of your car.Get in the car, turn on the Bluetooth® signal and GPS, open the App and enjoy a pleasant ride. WOOLF® Drive will work in background on your phone. The application allows you to monitor sensitive points such as speed cameras and traffic lights with cameras and receives updates when new points of interest are installed in the streets. The integrated mapping service in the device is the same as the one used by the most famous satellite navigators and by the major car manufacturers.WOOLF’s database covers 51 countries by detecting more than 100,000 speed cameras, and these numbers makes it the largest existing database.COMPONENTSThe WOOLF® Drive electronic card has been designed to ensure minimal encumbrance and hard-wearing over time. WOOLF® Drive has added to the best components available in the current industry a variety of treatments and solutions against sweat, humidity and high temperatures even during the summer. The rechargeable lithium ion battery installed on WOOLF® Drive has a capacity of 120mAh, and guarantees the operation of WOOLF® Drive for more than one month. The accelerometer allows WOOLF® Drive to turn off during inactivity, and to easily restart as soon as you get in the car. Thanks to the accelerometer, WOOLF® Drive recognizes your gestures and allows you to send alerts to other users. MAIN FEATURES
Accurate and discreet reporting: WOOLF® Drive guarantees you a prompt signalization close to the selected points of interest;
Ease of use: after the first matching phase you will no longer have to worry. Just get in the car, open the app and enjoy the pleasure of driving;
You will not need to download maps neither to set navigation routes;
Reminder of known speed cams: Although you may be aware of the position of speed cams in well-known areas, it may happen to be distracted and forget them, incurring in fines and sanctions. WOOLF® Drive will help you prevent this possibility. 
Validated Design: WOOLF® Drive has been designed after collecting the reviews of customers who have already used the bike version;
100% legal: WOOLF® Drive is a fully legal accessory, it is not a speed camera device because of its features and therefore it does not violate the Road Traffic Rules. 
